lead_paragraph: Paris ramped up its bid for the 2024 Olympics on Tuesday, securing about 8 million euros ($8.9 million) in four sponsorship deals and presenting its Eiffel Tower-shaped logo in a ceremony on the Champs Elysees.

headline.print_headline: Paris Secures Sponsors; Presents Logo for 2024 Olympic Bid
